STATES TO SHOW IN MOCKUP
Frame 1 — Prime lens selected
  Zoom rows (WIDE / TELE) hidden. Lens row shows only Prime spinbox.

Frame 2 — Zoom lens selected
  All four capture rows visible. Lens row shows Min–Max spinboxes.

Frame 3 — Log accordion open (add to either frame)
  Accordion expands to ~100 px showing grey monospace log lines.

Frame 4 — Captured state
  NEAR and FAR show white confirmed values. APPLY CALIBRATION button
  becomes fully bright (not dimmed).

